                  <h3> <strong class="Grey700">Art </strong> </h3>
                  <p>Art is the process of channeling emotions and ideas into creative expression. It allows us to
                    visually represent complex concepts and emotions that are hard to articulate. Engaging with art
                    enhances our understanding of the design process and opens up new perspectives. It lays the
                    groundwork for creating distinctive designs through the use of color, composition, and other
                    elements.
                  </p>

                </li>
                <div class="blankHXS"></div>

                <li class="progress__item" data-aos="fade-up">
                  <h3> <strong class="Grey700">Design </strong> </h3>
                  <p>In design, the core is a powerful creative vision that incorporates creativity, innovation,
                    meticulousness, and the capacity to think innovatively.
                  </p>

                </li>
                <div class="blankHXS"></div>

                <li class="progress__item" data-aos="fade-up">
                  <h3> <strong class="Grey700">Architecture </strong> </h3>
                  <p>Architecture involves crafting buildings that are functional and visually appealing, considering
                    the
                    users' needs, the interplay of various components, and the overall aesthetic. Success in
                    architecture
                    also means communicating effectively with clients and colleagues, and being organized and efficient.

                  </p>
                </li>
                <div class="blankHXS"></div>

                <li class="progress__item progress__item--active" data-aos="fade-up">
                  <h3> <strong>User experience design </strong> </h3>
                  <p>User experience design is about comprehending the user's desires and behaviors to create products
                    that are intuitive and fulfilling. It combines an attractive design with a user-friendly interface,
                    grounded in an understanding of human psychology and current technology trends.





                  </p>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
